  "instructions": [
    "In a medium pot, heat olive oil over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add onion and garlic; sauté for 3 minutes until translucent.",
    "Stir in french lentils, carrot, thyme, and cinnamon; cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add water and salt; bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 25 minutes until lentils are tender.",
    "Remove from heat; let sit covered for 5 minutes to thicken slightly.",
    "Adjust seasoning with salt and a pinch of sugar if needed."
